            <h3>Performance optimised compute: unparalleled computational performance with latest CPUs, more memory and more local SSD</h3>
            <p>G-series virtual machines feature latest <a href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=692100" target="_blank">Intel Xeon processor E5 v3 family</a>, two times more memory and four times more Solid State Drive storage (SSDs) than the D-series. G-series will provide unparalleled computational performance, more memory and more local SSD storage than any current VM size in the public cloud making it very ideal for your most demanding applications.</p>
<p>We have a new variant of the G-series sizes called GS that are specifically targeted for Premium Storage. The pricing and billing meters for the GS sizes are the same as G-series. SSD storage included in G-series VMs is local temporary storage. For persistent storage, use GS VMs instead and purchase Premium Storage separately.</p>
