            <h3>Optimised compute: 60% faster than A-series, more memory and local SSD</h3>
            <p>D-series virtual machines feature solid state drives (SSDs) and faster processors than the A-series and are also available for web or worker roles in Azure Cloud Services. This series is ideal for applications that demand faster CPUs, better local disk performance, or higher memories.</p>

