            <h3>License-included VMs</h3>
            <p>License-included Oracle virtual machines are Windows Server VMs with Oracle software preinstalled. The license for these VMs is provided by Microsoft Open Technologies, Inc. (MS Open Tech), a subsidiary of Microsoft Corp., under agreement with Oracle. When you choose this option, we charge separately for the Oracle software and the Windows Server virtual machines it runs on. The hourly rates shown here are just for the Oracle software license and do not include the cost of underlying Windows Server VMs. We bill for virtual machines by the minute.</p>
<p>Free trial, MSDN, BizSpark and Microsoft Partner Network member benefits (monetary credits) do not apply to license-included Oracle images, which are billed separately. However, if you are on a 6 or 12-Month Purchase Plan or the 12-Month Commitment Offer, your commitment balance can be used for Oracle license charges until 30th June 2016. Afterwards, license charges for the Oracle software will be billed separately and will not be discounted (consistent with all third-party products). Oracle license charges are billed separately for Enterprise Agreement customers and are not deducted from prepaid monetary commitment (consistent with all third-party products).</p>

