            <h3>Bring-Your-Own-License VMs</h3>
            <p>Another option in the Azure Marketplace is Bring-Your-Own-License (BYOL) Oracle images, which are Oracle Linux VMs with Oracle software preinstalled.</p>
<p>BYOL Oracle images do not include a license. If you deploy a BYOL Oracle image, you must have obtained license rights from Oracle or its authorised distributor. We charge only for the BYOL Linux VMs that the Oracle software runs on, not for the Oracle software itself (see pricing details under the "Linux" tab), so the prices shown here do not apply.</p>

            <h3>Oracle License Mobility Policy</h3>
            <p>The prices shown here also do not apply to Oracle software you install on any virtual machine under the Oracle License Mobility program. Oracle provides license mobility for customers who have already obtained a license from Oracle and want to run that software on Azure. To take advantage of this program, simply deploy a Windows Server or Linux VM and install your licensed Oracle software. For information, see the <a href="http://www.oracle.com/us/corporate/pricing/cloud-licensing-070579.pdf">Oracle Cloud Licensing Policy</a>.</p>

